    • combattre

      public void combattre(Creature c)
      Attack a creature according to the position of the target. If the distance is 1, then it is melee, otherwise it is long range. For each type of combat, we have a certain probability that the attack will fail, and if it fails, there is no damage. After a successful attack. The target object has a certain chance to succeed in defense, and if it succeeds, the damage is cut.
      Specified by:
      combattre in interface Combattant
      Parameters:
      c - Target creature of the attack.
